We are staring at a power-play by skilful Democrats, to not only reduce Presidential Executive Power, but at a transferring of power away from the people to the State to Big Brother, just like they seek to trash our 2nd Amendment. These Democrats are not one bit democratic, but are out and out Socialist Marxists. The long term play is to impose a Totalitarian system of government upon the people, just like all good little Socialists love to do. Sliding it in under the radar, scamming the populace with their fine gilded and noble talk of concern for the rights of the people, while stealing them from right under our very noses in the very same breath. A politic of stealth flown in through the back door on noble words disguising ignoble deeds, all so very underhanded. I hope every other American can see it. If they can't they need to, and quickly by familiarising themselves with basic law and basic precedents. The Democrats have lied on just about every point of law. The Republicans have not. This criminal Democratic Party must be dismantled and rebuilt.

We should all be grateful for the tenacity of Pat Cipollone, Jay Sekulow and deputies Michael Purpura and Patrick Philbin.  What a job Patrick Philbin has done and what is there about the White House business that he does not know.  Amazing, but he looks very tired today.  No wonder. He deserves a big hand. They all do, valiantly defending our Constitution.
